  ('heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-00090', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-111-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d30bcefc-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設經濟體系中有兩位消費者（A 和 B），兩種財貨（X 和 Y）。消費者 A 的初始稟賦為 （X=30,Y=20）而消費者 B的初始稟賦為（X=20,Y=30）。兩位消費者的效用函數皆為 U（X,Y）=X0.5Y0.5。均衡時兩位消費者的消費數量為何？', '["A（X=30,Y=20），B（X=20,Y=30）", "A（X=26,Y=24），B（X=24,Y=26）", "A（X=25,Y=25），B（X=25,Y=25）", "A（X=20,Y=30），B（X=30,Y=20）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7b2be102255d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "40ea3bc8eedf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "329", "s": "0908", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "企業管理"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-00091', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-111-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d30bcefc-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '若政府提高進口汽車關稅，下列敘述何者正確？', '["進口汽車銷售量增加", "進口汽車價格下跌", "國產汽車銷售量增加", "國產汽車價格下跌"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7b2be102255d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "40ea3bc8eedf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "329", "s": "0908", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "企業管理"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-00092', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-111-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d30bcefc-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '2016 年 10 月時，行政院為了推動長照 2.0 計畫，規劃以調高遺贈稅與菸稅來支應長照的財源需 求。依據財政部估計目前國內各種香菸平均售價約為65元，每包加收20元菸稅，則每年國人消 費的香菸將從原先 16.55 億包減少到 13.25 億包，根據上述資料計算消費香菸需求彈性之弧彈性 為何？', '["-0.17", "-0.65", "-0.83", "-1.05 32260、32560 32960、33060"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7b2be102255d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "40ea3bc8eedf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "329", "s": "0908", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "企業管理"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-00093', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-111-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d30bcefc-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '在其他條件不變之下，電動機車的供給下降，需求上升，則下列敘述何者正確？', '["均衡價格一定上漲", "均衡價格一定下跌", "均衡交易量一定上升", "均衡交易量一定下跌"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7b2be102255d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "40ea3bc8eedf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "329", "s": "0908", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "企業管理"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-00094', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-111-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d30bcefc-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設口罩市場的均衡數量與價格由供需雙方共同決定，其市場需求曲線為Qd=10-P，市場供給曲 線為Qs=P-2，其中P為口罩的價格，請問此時若政府對口罩市場中的價格制定價格上限P=5， 以下敘述何者正確？', '["政府制定價格上限後，消費者剩餘上升2.5", "政府制定價格上限後，消費者剩餘上升3.5", "政府制定價格上限後，消費者剩餘下降 3.5", "政府制定價格上限後，消費者剩餘下降2.5"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7b2be102255d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "40ea3bc8eedf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "329", "s": "0908", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "企業管理"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-00095', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-111-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d30bcefc-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '某工廠之生產函數為Q(L,K)=L0.8K0.2，其中Q為產量，L與K分別為勞動與資本，每單位勞動 價格為1，每單位資本價格為2，請問在成本極小化之目標下，投入勞動和資本的最適比例（L/K） 為何？', '["4", "0.25", "8", "0.125"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7b2be102255d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "40ea3bc8eedf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "329", "s": "0908", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "企業管理"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-00096', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-111-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d30bcefc-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '兩家電信公司的長途通話費可以設定為每分鐘$3或$4，下表顯示報償矩陣。則A、B廠商的優勢 策略分別為何？ A廠商的策略 $4 $3 $320萬 $500萬 $4 $320萬 $200萬 B廠商的策略 $200萬 $450萬 $3 $500萬 $450萬', '["$3；$3", "$3；$4", "$4；$3", "$4；$4"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7b2be102255d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "40ea3bc8eedf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "329", "s": "0908", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "企業管理"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-00097', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-111-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d30bcefc-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關獨占之敘述，下列何者正確？', '["航空公司對於頭等艙與經濟艙訂定不同票價，係因其採取差別定價", "因為供給量與市場價格不存在一對一關係，所以獨占廠商無供給曲線", "與完全競爭的廠商相比，獨占廠商的產量較多，售價較低", "獨占廠商利潤極大點須滿足「產品價格等於邊際成本」條件"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7b2be102255d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "40ea3bc8eedf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "329", "s": "0908", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "企業管理"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-00098', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-111-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d30bcefc-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設在某一個國家，其15歲以上的人口為500,000人，勞動力人口為300,000人。在勞動力人口 中，就業人口為240,000人，失業人口為60,000。請問勞動參與率為何？', '["25%", "48%", "55%", "60% 32260、32560 32960、33060"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7b2be102255d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "40ea3bc8eedf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "329", "s": "0908", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "企業管理"}'::jsonb, NULL)
